<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.271534>
    dc:description "FIGURE 26. Neopicobia spp. female. N. ictericus (Skoracki and Glowska, 2010) (A – D). A, apodemes I and II; B, propodonotal shield; C, region of setal base d 1; D, pygidial shield. N. carpodacus (Skoracki et al., 2010) (E, F). E, pygidial shield; F, coxal fields III and IV. N. modularis (Skoracki and Magowski, 2001) (G). G, coxal fields III and IV. N. cardinalis (Skoracki et al., 2010) (H – K). H, coxal fields III and IV; I, propodonotal shield; J, pygidial shield; K, region of setal base d 1. N. troglodytes (Skoracki et al., 2010) (L). L, pygidial shield." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/271534/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

